title: PML-N candidate Arshad Malik wins PP-200 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz candidate Muhammad Arshad Malik has won the election for Punjab Assembly from PP-200, Sahiwal III by securing 48871 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was an independent candidate Ahmad Ali, who bagged 37757 votes.
The votersâ€™ turn-out remained 51.62 per cent.
